query:
SELECT 
  c.name as categoryName,
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.imageUrl) as uniqueImageUrls,
  COUNT(p.id) as totalProducts,
  p.imageUrl as sampleImageUrl
FROM products p
JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id
WHERE c.slug IN ('gc-columns', 'guard-columns', 'spe-cartridges', 'filtration', 'chromatography-supplies')
GROUP BY c.name, p.imageUrl
LIMIT 20;
